": "606d7f"}, "abstract": "清光绪年间，山河动荡，外忧内患，中国处在生死存亡的一线间。光绪皇帝（舒适 饰）当朝，却因慈禧太后（唐若青 饰）垂帘听政，身不由己，宛如傀儡一般。户部尚书翁同龢习光绪学经解义，并灌输启蒙思想，使光绪萌发变法之心；而光绪宠妃珍妃（周璇 饰）亦每日存下银两，以作军资。 甲午惨败，翁同龢开缺回乡，临别前向光绪举荐康有为。戊戌年（1898年），光绪与维新派展开变法，却受到慈禧为首的顽固派的抵制，双方矛盾愈演愈烈。太后一方定下计谋，企图借天津阅兵之际废掉光绪；而维新一派亦相时而动，派出袁世凯（罗维 饰）刺杀荣禄，围执太后……", "description": "", "tags": [], "cover_url": "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2607019041.jpg", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p1150291488.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2227613527.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p1187023730.jpg", "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2152268851.jpg"], "actions": ["可播放"], "sharing_url": "https://www.douban.com/doubanapp/dispatch/movie/1439106", "honor_infos": [{"kind": "movie", "uri": "douban://douban.com/subject_collection/ECPYOEZNY?type=rank&category=movie&rank_type=film_genre", "rank": 15, "title": "中国香港历史片榜"}], "good_rating_stats": 0, "subtype": "movie", "null_rating_reason": ""}}, {"item_type": "movie", "id": "1304787", "rank": 16, "name": "瀛台泣血", "names": [], "links": ["https://movie.douban.com/subject/1304787/", "douban://douban.com/movie/1304787"], "covers": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2457478969.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2457478969.jpg"], "rating": {"count": 2650, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.3}, "score": 7.3, "vote": 2650, "summary": "1976 / 中国香港 / 剧情 历史 古装 / 李翰祥 / 狄龙 卢燕", "ext": {"comment": "", "controversy_reason": "", "rank_value": 16, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2457478969.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2457478969.jpg"}, "is_show": false, "vendor_icons": ["https://img2.doubanio.com/f/frodo/8e1b7f8b48804cf759fc411e75d62c5ffd4f8f42/pics/vendors/migu_video.png", "https://img9.doubanio.com/f/frodo/88a62f5e0cf9981c910e60f4421c3e66aac2c9bc/pics/vendors/bili